{"title_page": "Thakarius Keyes", "text_new": "{{short description|American football cornerback}}\n{{Infobox NFL biography\n| name                = Thakarius Keyes\n| image               = \n| image_size          = \n| alt                 = \n| caption             = \n| number              = \n| current_team        = Kansas City Chiefs\n| position            = [[Cornerback]]\n| birth_date          = \n| birth_place         = \n| height_ft           = 6\n| height_in           = 1\n| weight_lb           = 200\n| high_school         = [[Laurel High School (Mississippi)|Laurel]]<br>([[Laurel, Mississippi]])\n| college             = [[Tulane Green Wave football|Tulane]]\n| draftyear           = 2020\n| draftround          = 7\n| draftpick           = 237\n| pastteams           = \n* [[Kansas City Chiefs]] ({{NFL Year|2020}}\u2013present)\n| status              = Unsigned draft pick\n| highlights          = \n| statleague          = NFL\n| statseason          = \n| statweek            = \n| statlabel1          = \n| statvalue1          = \n| statlabel2          = \n| statvalue2          = \n| statlabel3          = \n| statvalue3          = \n| nflnew              = \n| pfr                 = \n}}\n\n'''Thakarius Keyes''' is an [[American football]] [[cornerback]] for the [[Kansas City Chiefs]] of the [[National Football League]] (NFL). He played [[college football]] at [[Tulane Green Wave football|Tulane]].\n\nIn 2019, Keyes started every game for Tulane and held opposing quarterbacks to a 45 percent completion percentage rate when he was targeted. He was an Honorable Mention All-[[American Athletic Conference]] honoree.<ref>{{cite news |title=Tulane DB Thakarius Keyes Selected by Kansas City in 2020 NFL Draft |url=https://wgno.com/sports/tulane-db-thakarius-keyes-selected-by-kansas-city-in-2020-nfl-draft/ |accessdate=April 25, 2020 |work=WGNO |date=April 25, 2020}}</ref> In his junior and senior seasons, Keyes had 85 tackles, 18 passes defended and two interceptions.<ref>